Global Kitchen Sink & Faucet Services Market Insights
Kitchen Sink & Faucet Services Market size was valued at USD 15.4 Billion in 2022 and is projected to reach USD 22.3 Billion by 2030, growing at a CAGR of 5.2% from 2024 to 2030.

Kitchen Sink & Faucet Services Market Overview
The global market for kitchen sink and faucet services was valued at USD 5.2 billion in 2023 and is projected to reach USD 8.4 billion by 2032, growing at a compound annual growth rate (CAGR) of 5.5% during the forecast period. This growth is primarily driven by increasing home renovation activities, rising disposable incomes, and the growing awareness about modern plumbing solutions. The market is also being propelled by the increasing demand for smart and touchless faucets, which offer convenience and water-saving benefits.

